name: DLF Westend Heights New Town
desc:
About the Project - DLF Westend Heights New Town by DLF
Welcome to DLF Westend Heights New Town by DLF, a prestigious residential project located in DLF Newtown, Akshayanagar, Bangalore. This project is ready to move in, so you can start enjoying your new home right away. The project offers spacious 2 and 3 BHK apartments with an area ranging from 1225 to 1820 sq.ft. With a total of 19 towers and 1870 units, you'll have plenty of options to choose from.DLF Westend Heights New Town is designed to provide you with a comfortable and luxurious living experience. Plus, you have the convenience of availing home loans from HDFC to make your dream home a reality.There are 1870 units of 2, 3 BHK Apartments for sale in DLF Westend Heights New Town, DLF Newtown, Akshayanagar, Bangalore, spread across 19 towers.

About the Builder - DLF
DLF is a renowned name in the real estate industry with a strong track record of delivering high-quality projects. With years of experience and expertise, DLF has earned the trust and respect of homebuyers. Their commitment to excellence is evident in every aspect of their projects, from construction to amenities.

About the Locality - DLF Newtown, Akshayanagar, Bangalore
DLF Newtown, Akshayanagar, Bangalore is a prime location that offers a host of amenities and conveniences. You'll find several renowned schools such as PES Public School, The Salonee Public School, and St Ann's School in the vicinity, ensuring that your children receive the best education. For your healthcare needs, there are hospitals like Jayashree Multi Speciality Hospital, Akshaya Hospital, and New Sri Sai Hospital nearby.The locality is well-connected to the main highway, making commuting a breeze. Additionally, you'll find shopping malls like Specality Centre and Pranaojas Healthcare for all your retail therapy needs. With easy access to metro stations and other public transportation, getting around the city is convenient.

Project Amenities
DLF Westend Heights New Town offers a range of amenities to enhance your lifestyle. The project is spread across 11 acres and is loaded with amenities like a club house, rainwater harvesting, a reflexology park, a children's play area, 24x7 water supply, a card room, a spa, billiards/snooker table, an intercom, CCTV surveillance, a banquet hall, internet/Wi-Fi connectivity, a squash court, a tennis court, vaastu compliance, a multipurpose room, power backup, a cycling & jogging track, a gymnasium, a swimming pool, lifts, and 24x7 security.With its perfect combination of contemporary architecture and features, DLF Westend Heights New Town offers you a comfortable and luxurious living experience. So, come and be a part of this exquisite residential project and make your dream home a reality.

OVERVIEW OF EPITOME ELAN - Benchmark for Luxury Living!

Poised in South Bengaluru, Epitome Elan’s integrated concept offers a unique combination that delivers the comfort of an independent home along with a superlative lifestyle and secure environment of an apartment to suit the aspirations of modern families!

Spread out over a sprawling 2.5 acre property, the project offers 2 BHK & 3 BHK apartments starting from 1275sqft to 2050sqft with highest carpet area efficiency in the segment. Unmatched quality and value are accomplished through an integrated modern living concept, top of the line specifications, fittings & fixtures from international brands, and modular construction technology for speed, strength and stability. The unique architectural features of Epitome Elan include functional design and space planning for maximum natural lighting & ventilation, exquisite landscaped areas and large sit-out areas, and dry & wet concepts in kitchens and bathrooms.

Epitome Elan stays smart, secure and future ready via digital locks with biometric keyless entry along with video intercom system for screening, smart card access & surveillance in all common areas with Tier-5 security, and provision for home automation, fire & gas leakage alarm system and charging bay for electric vehicles. The aspects of eco-friendly and sustainable living are achieved through LED lighting in common areas, solar lighting for outdoor areas, sewage treatment plant, water softening plant, rainwater harvesting, gas bank, waste management system, and organic waste converter.

Epitome Elan provides the Luxury lifestyle & convenience through resort inspired amenities for wellness & entertainment, crèche, convenience store, café with working space, unisex salon, Laundromat, ATM and other facilities.

In a nutshell, making Elan your home will guarantee you an exclusive lifestyle that combines the convenience of city living with the charm of resort living at one of the most sought-after residential localities in Bangalore. Property for sale in JP Nagar 6th Phase, Bangalore. This project, that is, Aryan Auqilaa is a well designed project by Karsten Homes (P)  Ltd. It is offering Ready to Move units. If you are looking at Apartment, you should check out Aryan Auqilaa. Available configurations include 3 BHK. As per the area plan, units are in the size range of 1264.0 - 1805.0 sq.ft.. Aryan Auqilaa was launched in November 2015. Project possession is slated for Dec, 2015. There is 1 building in this project. Total number of flats at Aryan Auqilaa is 48. Aryan Auqilaa is located in Puttenahalli Road, KR Layout, Near Chitrakalaa Arts and Crafts, JP Nagar Phase VI. There are 48 units in this residential project.

Come home to Aryan Auqilaa. It offers multiple facilities such as Power Backup. There is Security Guards. These amenities make this property totally aspirational.

Major banks such as HDFC, LIC Housing Finance, Punjab National Bank have approved financing for Aryan Auqilaa.

Karsten Homes (P)  Ltd is a renowned name in the real estate space. Founded in 2009, the company has developed as many as 10 projects.

Social infrastructure like banks, schools and parks surround JP Nagar area. It is also very well-connected to various parts of the city by public transport network.

name: Hyde Park
desc:
About the Project - Hyde Park by Nitesh Estates:
Hyde Park by Nitesh Estates is an exciting residential project located in Hulimavu, Bangalore. With a Ready to Move, this project offers spacious 3 BHK Apartments ranging from 1642 to 1920 sq.ft. In total, there are 501 units spread across 6 towers. Home loans are available through HDFC for those interested in financing their dream home.Located in the vibrant neighborhood of Hulimavu, Bangalore, Hyde Park offers a convenient and comfortable lifestyle. The area is well-connected and features a range of amenities for residents. Nearby hospitals include Medax Hospitals Gottigere, Sri Krishna Hospital, Fortis International Care, Noble Multispeciality Hospitals, and Sri Sairam Hospital. For education, there are several schools and colleges in the vicinity such as Government Model Primary School, St. Peter's School, The American School, Loyola Higher Primary School, and Hulimavu College. Shopping enthusiasts can enjoy their time at Royal Meenakshi Mall and Janaka Shopping Complex. The project is also conveniently located near the main highway, making commuting a breeze.Hyde Park by Nitesh Estates offers a host of amenities designed to enhance your living experience. The project boasts a multipurpose hall, lawn tennis court, sun deck, party lawn, laundromat, piped gas connection, gazebo, 24x7 water supply, car parking, intercom, club house, CCTV, solid waste management and disposal, shopping mall, vaastu compliant, staff quarter, multipurpose room, conference room, fire fighting system, amphitheater, indoor games, skating rink, yoga/meditation area, tennis court, basketball court, gated community, community hall, library, children's play area, rainwater harvesting, ATM, 24x7 security, swimming pool, gymnasium, cycling & jogging track, power backup, and lift(s).Nitesh Estates, the builder behind Hyde Park, is a renowned name in the real estate industry. Established in 1999, they have a strong track record of delivering quality projects that meet the needs and aspirations of their customers.Experience the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and luxury at Hyde Park by Nitesh Estates in Hulimavu, Bangalore. Don't miss out on the opportunity to own your dream home in this modern development. Contact us today to learn more and book your new home.

name: Esteem Kings Court
desc:
RERA ID - PRM/KA/RERA/1251/310/PR/181122/002159

Esteem Group welcomes you to the royal abode for majestic living - ESTEEM KING'S COURT. The project has been conceptualized to combine the feeling of royalty with modern architecture, thereby creating a unique experience for its residents. A low-rise structure with stately courtyards creates a vintage essence; while the modern amenities, prime location and picturesque surroundings make it the design of a new era.

name: Valmark City Ville
desc: Valmark CityVille offers you homes that takes you back in time to the winsome days when homes nestled in greenery, natural comforts were numerous, a sense of peace ruled, simple pleasures abounded and happiness was real. Offering you a lake-front villa living experience of leaving every unpleasant aspect of the city far behind, it is a meeting of the world that was and the world that will be. Without having to leave the city even a wee bit behind, here you enjoy a host of natural assets that yield a great sense of well-being and unalloyed joy. It is a world that you can only reluctantly step out of. Valmark CityVille invites you to a world that is a giant step forward in wholesome and luxurious living.

name: Valmark Orchard Square
